# Optional. A GitHub personal access token (classic, no scopes needed for
# public data). Without it the app still works: it starts on the bundled
# sample profile and charts real usernames anonymously through the REST
# API (about 60 lookups per hour per IP). A token switches to GraphQL
# with far higher limits and GitHub's exact language colors.
#
# Never commit this file's real counterpart (.env is gitignored), and do
# not set this variable in a public deployment: a Vite env var is bundled
# into the shipped JavaScript where anyone can read it.
VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=
